name: I For Innocence
description:
It's a digital painting by Mrs H.Pasandideh as a member of Sepas art group.

There is sorrow and captivity in her innocent and beautiful eyes. But she has not yet lost her strength and endurance in the face of the oppressors of his time and has turned her back on them.
Good and bright days are on the way...

It's for Afghan girls, wishing them freedom.
